{"word":"στρατοπεδεύω","slug":"στρατοπεδεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στρατοπεδεύω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to encamp, bivouac, take up a position</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:<p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <el>στρατοπεδεύομαι</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>ἐστρατοπεδεῦσθαι</el> <i>to be in camp</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: of a fleet, <i>to be stationed</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}